body_html: I would like to help, but this kind of open-ended question without providing the background information requested in the issues reporting template poses the prospect that it may take me a long time to run through the codelab myself, in a setup different in unknown ways from yours, and not discover any problem. This forum is intended for well-characterized bug reports and feature requests. Usage difficulties should be posted to stackoverflow.
